Added android:layout_gravity="top" to SlidingThumbImageView tag
Initialize 'added' array in getMiniApps method. Added code to keep contact mini-app open when cursor moves beyond proper name.
Set phrase prediction initially unchecked in settings. Trim proper nouns before sending to mini-app.
Moved key click to action up state and long pressed method. Fixed bug with smiley side keyboard not displaying correct characters and turning image green.
Added save/restore paint style and stroke width in drawPathLine method.
Added MessageLogger class to report exceptions.
Modified code to allow Calendar Reach to remain available for any valid terms in last 8 words.
Reduced vertical gap between keys. Added bottom spacing to key labels.
Sync the location of mini-app icon on mini-app actionbar with index in internal mini-app list.
Added checks for null in removePreviousMiniApps() method.
Adjusted key sizes, positions and spacing. Added new category for Contact mini-app.
Set large font as default. Modified font preference labelling.
Fixed key popup window for horizontal orientation.
Added code to prevent duplicate words appearing in suggestion view. Code clean-up in same section.
Changed text color for key preview windows.
Increased widths of popup keys.

Added code to set popup key height to keyboard key height.
Increased height and font size for preview windows.
Added code to prevent overlap of suggestion view when initially displayed.
Removed any "..." from pred string in pickSuggestionManuallyLatin() method.
After loading mini-app icons during service connection, added code to call inputService.updateCandidates() to refresh mini-app bar.

Fixed bug where multiple icons of same mini-app appeared in action bars.
Set Correction Indication default to false. Decreased size of flash area.
Changes mini app action bar color. Added indicator arrow for selected mini app.
